description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '20 Minute Bodyweight Leg Workout | Calisthenics Giant Sets' from the channel Caroline Girvan.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: We will be using the giant set format that you all probably love by now if you have been training with me for awhile! 

The timer will be on for 30 seconds per exercise and within each giant set there are 4 exercises so 2 minutes in total of work before we have 20 seconds rest! 

Every 1st and 3rd then 2nd and 4th set will be the same exercise!

All you will need for this bodyweight leg workout is a chair for Bulgarian lunges, a yoga block and your mat!

REAR STEP
ELEVATED LUNGE
REAR STEP

CURTSEY LUNGE TO STAND
